      "id": "c3a71220_921a436b",
      "file_path": "Dockerfile",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 2,
      "message": "Sure, We removed the manually pin and download a specific Go version (ENV GOLANG_VERSION=1.25.5). And also we have few critical issues in GoLang 1.25.5, So we are using golang:alpine image.\nAnd Also to make the image clean and simple in runtime we separated build and run stage.",
