      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 2,
      "message": "You are removing helm from the final image. The first stage is completely useless from my perspective. Sure, you are \"solving\" the vulnerabilities by just not installing helm in the image anymore, but arguably it should still be included.\nI would rather suggest to not build helm from source and rather just install it via `apk add`.\nSo please revert the multistage aspect of your CR",
